30:27.854 --> 30:35.443
the Corps marched on his house to try to revolt?

30:38.292 --> 30:48.481
He was trying to crack down on them to quit hazing 
the freshmen so long, and they tried to confront

30:38.292 --> 30:48.481
him. Where was he? He was in the college residence 
up there? He was living in the president's house,

30:53.625 --> 30:57.248
yes, sir, and they marched on that house one night. 
