We knew for a fact that they were going to do two 
things. They were going to let the niggers in, and

31:17.080 --> 31:21.364
they were going to let the women in. I made a million 
old men mad, because I said, which do you want

31:21.384 --> 31:26.550
first? You want the nigger in there, or you want the 
nigger in there? You want the woman in there. And,

31:31.315 --> 31:33.477
